sources.title: Monstrosity 1963 (Horror, Sci-Fi) Bodies for sale! Starring Marjorie Eaton, Frank Gerstle,
sources.description:
In the Name of Science, Fear Has a New Face!
In a quest for eternal youth, a wealthy old woman employs a scientist who performs brain transplants, resulting in horrifying consequences. "The Atomic Brain" unveils the gruesome outcomes as the victims of these experiments fight for their lives against unimaginable horrors.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/UX1EamYbqXc


Original title: Monstrosity (1963) 
Alternative titles: The Atomic Brain, O Cérebro Atômico, 原子头
This movie is subtitled in many languages.

Directors: Joseph V. Mascelli, Jack Pollexfen
Writers: Vy Russell, Sue Dwiggins 
Genres: Horror, Mystery, Sci-Fi
Cast: Marjorie Eaton, Frank Gerstle, Frank Fowler, Erika Peters, Judy Bamber, Lisa Lang, Xerxes the Cat 
Budget: $40,000
